Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat? So lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the end of Act 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For Tenorio's big guns,\Nthat was pretty meh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hear the next one is the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess we can\Nlook forward to Act 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:01.44,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Decisions and Duels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For not being able to swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the one\Nwho should be apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragging you into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they sure are huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm so sorry! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... By huge, I\Nmeant this ballast area...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That dragon... it seems just like\Nthe little ones aboveground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that this really isn't\Nany time to complain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, uh-huh. I'm totally fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we're kind of in a sticky\Nsituation here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if I'm hindering you,\Nthen please let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you should get hurt because of me,\NAmagiri-senpai... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Toudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else paying the price\Nbecause of the likes of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... but!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you'd mop up the floor\Nwith an opponent like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So wouldn't it only be fair\Nto believe in me a little more,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,since I put up a good fight against you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever say "the likes of me" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so gentle and strong...\Na lovely young girl, Toudou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's just like the ones up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou, can you get a read\Non that thing's Prana flow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I mean, it's a little vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be constantly\Nmoving inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess my only\Noption is to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Till now, I never had a Lux\Nthat could withstand my Prana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet this one can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri-senpai? Amagiri-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're only able to fight at full throttle\Nup to five minutes or so, Amagiri-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I really push it, I think\NI can go a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Amagiri-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,why would you go that far to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I want to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean Riessfeld-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So of course... uh...\Num... Amagiri-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're in love with\NRiessfeld-senpai, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, sure, as a person\NI do admire her... but see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... then... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I apologize for asking\Na silly question like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I still have a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, isn't the rescue squad\Ntaking a long time to get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you fighting here, Toudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to save my father\Nwho's being detained as a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago, someone broke into a shop\Nmy father and I happened to be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in trying to save me\Nwhen I was taken hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ended up killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, he would've\Ngotten off for self-defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but my father was a Genestella.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the charges were more serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But looking back now, even at age eight,\NI could've taken the kidnapper out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was a coward, and I just froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I do something, my father won't\Nbe released for several decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was when my uncle told me\Nthere was just one way to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you came to Asterisk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have any choice\Nbut to throw myself at my uncle's mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I do what he says,\NI have nothing to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the path you chose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you go on like this, sooner\Nor later you'll hit a brick wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, I only\Njust realized that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But me, on my own? I can't possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's just no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone, Toudou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least,\Nyou have me to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's a path that\Nyou've chosen yourself, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That I've chosen myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm the one who should be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you stroke\Nmy head a lot, Amagiri-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess you don't like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father used to stroke\Nmy head just like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For God's sake, don't\Nmake me worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Anyway,\Nabout your next opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before you go any further,\Nmay I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, you said that\Nyou were worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But were you worried\Nabout Kirin Toudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or Kirin Toudou, a mere\Ntool in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I need from you is\Nyour power, nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you were just with\Nthat Ser Veresta wielder, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear he recently caused\Nsome kind of row with Allekant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a hassle if he dragged you\Ninto any unnecessary trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have anything\Nmore to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:10:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri-senpai taught me\Nsomething very valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I believe that there's still a lot\Nthat I should learn from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a load of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do is\Nexactly what I tell you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you dare defy me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think made you Rank #1?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think Asterisk's a joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without my help, you don't\Nstand a chance in hell of winning a Festa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's probably beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then shut up and just do what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to save\Nyour father as soon as possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But neither do I think that I can\Naccomplish that your way, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a smartass, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful to you for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I've made up my mind\Nto fight my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll regret it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think you're going to\Nget along on your own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First, I think I'll take\Nsomeone on in a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An opponent of my own choosing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the decision will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for complying\Nwith my ill-mannered request.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it's all good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,why a duel with me, of all things?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I felt that it was absolutely necessary\Nfor me to take my true first step here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True first step?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if we're gonna do this,\Nthen I'm going all-out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not like I didn't\Ngo all-out last time, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to use that Ogre Lux?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't keep up with your\Nspeed using the Ser Veresta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose the same way, no way\Nis Julis going to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to make some adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be looking forward to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely they didn't have to go out of\Ntheir way to provide such a stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but this is a must-see match,\Nso why wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry so much, Riessfeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou is formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of just sword skills,\Nshe might be a cut above Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato's taken on a way more\Npowerful opponent before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-nee... Ayato's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the guy does seem to\Nhave some kind of plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to lend him a Lux. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So he asked you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that he asked you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's about to start, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Start of the duel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected of you,\NAmagiri-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was like thrusting\Nagainst thick steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the one thing I'm sure about is\Nthe amount of my Prana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but... that's the first time\Nanyone's evaded my Conjoined Cranes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that was Conjoined Cranes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:34.59,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NESTING STATE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesting State.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:35.84,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CITRUS BLOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Citrus Bloom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.10,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SIDE-BY-SIDE WINGS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Side-by-side Wings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.56,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLUE SEA WAVE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue Sea Wave...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Toudou Style boasts\N49 different conjoined skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and combining them results\Nin the foolproof multi-hit attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Conjoined Cranes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Conjoined Cranes are invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I will finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, I guess I'll\Nrespond to that by going all-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His Météo arts failed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei-style Spear Skill -\NNinth Cloud Wasp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.02,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AMAGIRI SHINMEI-STYLE SPEAR SKILL -\NNINTH CLOUD WASP
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spear Skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I surprise you at least a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a tricky move for a tricky move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The more tricky moves\Nyou've got, the trickier it gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei-style\NShort Sword Technique...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reaper!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I win!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei-style Grappling Skill...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Purifying Sweep!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Toudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both the shield and the short\Nsword were decoys, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been soundly defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}End of duel! Winner...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:30.33,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AYATO AMAGIRI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato Amagiri!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew that you'd really win?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Ayato.\NYou were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato? May I come in?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me for the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um... excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You, too, Toudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It seems that she has\Nsome business here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind letting me\Njoin your practice sessions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You see, Amagiri-senpai\Ninvited me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at the time, I had to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's news to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but look, if someone of\NToudou's caliber joined us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that would give us\Na range of options, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you do have a point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I don't mind. Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide on your own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And come to think of it, you've been infiltrating\Nour practice sessions day after day yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Riessfeld, you're such a nitpicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little is the way of\Nthe world. Just give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you call usurping, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is our lineup,\Nbut are you still game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kirin! I know you're in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come out of there, Kirin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, open this door!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin, what kind of an idiot are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After dueling someone\Nwithout my permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you end up losing\Nin such a humiliating manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's clear to you now, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need my assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I've made up my mind\Nto fight my way from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do is\Nobey my every order!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's already taken the first\Nstep with her own two feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have no business\Nbutting in anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a Genestella, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You sure about this, Kirin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who covered up\Nyour father's deeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse to come back to me,\NI'll spread the word on everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, what an intriguing thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the... E-Enfield...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of meddling\Nin your relationship with Kirin Toudou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she is also a student\Nat Seidoukan Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does that make her\Nan asset to this school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but also to the Integrated\NEnterprise Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you intend to corrupt her\Nwith your self-interest in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can ill afford to look the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure my mother would\Nmake the same judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate what you've done\Nfor me. That's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it hadn't been for you, I never\Nwould've come to Asterisk,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I wouldn't have\Nmet these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so... for all you've done...\Nall you've done till now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you from the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to\Ntraining with you, Toudou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Amagiri-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... there's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no, I mean two favors\NI'd like to ask of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Favors?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to call you by your\Nfirst name, Amagiri-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that all? Sure, of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayato-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Will you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,call me by my first name, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, Kirin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, want to join us\Nnext time we practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'd like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only agreed to do this because\Nyou said it was a puppet test!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You never said we'd have to\Nfight something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, that's the deal, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess our victory isn't\Njust a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! As if I was gunning\Nfor anything less from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I was able to nab some data on that\Nyoung swordsman - our only red flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was so incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's enough to make me drool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Tenorio Faction will\Nhave lost face with this failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you've acquired this data\Nwithout having to go after it yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so it's killing two birds\Nwith one stone, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Seidoukan Academy\Nand everyone in Tenorio,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for exerting yourselves\Nin so many ways for my sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the curtain will\Ngo up for the main attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay with us till the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that you, Sasamiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're fighting\Nfor your father's sake. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, it is.
